'''Thanatizine''' was a drug that would put an individual into a state close to [[Suspended animation/Legends|suspended animation]]. In such a state, a [[Human/Legends|Human]] would breathe around ten times an [[Standard hour/Legends|hour]], and have a [[Heart/Legends|heartrate]] of less than a beat per [[Standard minute/Legends|minute]].

On [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]], it was used to slow down the effects of developing [[Fever wasp/Legends|fever wasps]] so they could be removed.

Another generation of the drug, [[Thanatizine II]], was utilized by [[Cronal]].

